(7, 58, '上海市工程图学学会成立三十周年庆祝大会隆重举行', '2014-07-31-06-29-06', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">上海市工程图学学会成立三十周年庆祝大会暨八届二次会员代表大会、上海市工程图学学会2011年学术年会于12月24日在东华大学第三教学大楼二楼演讲厅隆重举行。上海市科协秘书长王晓东、东华大学校长助理柯勤飞教授、江苏省工程图学学会副理事长卢章平教授等出席了大会。到会代表近200人。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 18px;" align="center"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold;"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B75.jpg" alt="" width="504" height="380" border="0" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold;"><br />    </span><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">庆祝大会由学会副理事长林大钧教授主持，杨建国理事长首先做了工作报告，他回顾了学会三十年来的风雨历程，感谢老一辈学会创始人对学会的巨大贡献，介绍了本届理事会近两年所做的工作，并且又展望了学会明天更加美好的前景。接着学会的老领导、原第四届理事会理事长朱辉教授发言，学会老会员代表石娟教授、学会新会员代表李振宇同学也相继发言，大家都对学会的发展寄予了厚望。兄弟省市学会代表卢章平教授作了热情洋溢的发言，他肯定了三十年来上海市工程图学学会对我国图学研究和发展所做的贡献，并期望学会有更加卓越的进步和发展。会上又宣读了中国图学学会对大会的贺词。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 18px;" align="center"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold;"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B76.jpg" alt="" width="470" height="357" border="0" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">东华大学校长助理柯勤飞教授代表学校对大会的召开表示热烈祝贺，希望学会今后有更大的发展。最后，上海市科协王晓东秘书长作了重要发言，他肯定了上海市工程图学学会所取得的成绩，勉励大家继续努力，在上海地区乃至在全国发挥更大的作用。庆祝大会以后在八届二次会员代表大会上又通过了关于学会更名等几项决议。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 18px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B77.jpg" alt="" width="473" height="361" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 18px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B78.jpg" alt="" width="242" height="253" border="0" /><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold;"><br />   </span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 18px;" align="left"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">下午12:30 2011年学术年会在二楼演讲厅召开，大会由李金海秘书长主持，杨建国、林大钧、蒋丹教授及欧特克（上海）公司陈文君工程师分别作了学术报告，大会报告以后又分成三个分会场进行了专题学术交流报告。生动的报告吸引了广大会员，会后不少会员对本次学术年会一致作出好评，学术报告给他们留下了难忘的回忆。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B79.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="305" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B710.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="370" border="0" /></p>', '', 1, 10, '2014-07-31 06:29:06', 550, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-07-31 06:29:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 1, 15, '', '', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(8, 59, '上海市工程图学学会获二星级学会光荣称号', '2014-07-31-06-31-53', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: large;">上海市工程图学学会申报参加2011年上海市科协星级学会评估活动，经审核、公示等程序，被评为二星级学会，这是我们学会成立三十年来工作积淀和本届理事会带领广大会员共同努力的结果。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: large;">9月26日，由上海市科协及所属学会、协会、研究会，基层科协的广大科技工作者共同参与的“上海市科协第九届学术年会”在上海科学会堂举行。开幕式上，市科协主席沈文庆院士，市工程师学会理事长翁史烈院士分别致词。市科协副主席孙正心宣读了《关于2011年上海市科学技术协会星级学会评估及复查结果的决定》。市政协副主席、市科协副主席高小玫，市科技党委副书记陈龙为2011年上海市科学技术协会星级学会颁发证书。学会李金海秘书长上台从陈龙副书记手中接过二星级学会证书。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 18px;"> </p>\r\n', '\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 18px;"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: large;">成绩只能说明过去，希望全体会员再接再厉，争取在2013年学会换届之年获得星级学会的的最高级——三星级学会。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B71.jpg" alt="" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt;">市科协主席沈文庆院士致开幕词</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 18px;" align="center"><span lang="EN-US"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B72.jpg" alt="" border="0" /> </span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt;">学会李金海秘书长从陈龙副书记手中接受星级证书</span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B73.jpg" alt="" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt;">星级学会颁证仪式</span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B74.jpg" alt="" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt;">部分学会会员获证后留影</span></p>', 1, 10, '2014-07-31 06:31:53', 550, '', '2014-07-31 06:32:41', 550, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-07-31 06:31:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 2, 14, '', '', 1, 1, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
