(16, 68, '第三届中国图学大会（China Graphics’2011）征文通知', 'china-graphics-2011', '<p class="MsoPlainText" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 3.9pt;" align="left"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">第三届中国图学大会（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">China Graphics</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">’</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">2011</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">）将于</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">2011</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">8</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">月中旬在美丽的天府之国</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">--</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">四川省成都市召开。作为中国图学界最高级别的学术会议，这是一次全国从事图学研究、教学与应用的一线工作者交流经验的大会；也是一次全国从事数字化设计、数字化制造、数字化服务以及制造业信息化的一线工作者交流经验的大会。中国图学大会自创办以来每两年举行一次，为与会学者提供广泛的学术交流平台。</span></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p class="MsoPlainText" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 3.9pt;" align="left"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoPlainText" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: 24px; margin-top: 7.8pt;" align="left"><span style="font-size: 15pt; line-height: 30px; font-family: 黑体;">一、大会主题</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoPlainText" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 3.9pt;" align="left"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">第三届中国图学大会（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">China Graphics</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">’</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">2011</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">）以“图学与产品全生命周期数字化技术”为主题，会议就图学科学与技术、图学应用与教育以及以图学为基础的产品全生命周期数字化技术等方面的理论、方法、技术和应用等专题开展研讨与交流。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoPlainText" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 3.9pt;" align="left"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">会议将邀请著名学者就图学与产品全生命周期数字化技术的最新动态和热点问题做专题讲演和报告，同时举办相关的专题研讨会。欢迎广大教学、科研工作者、企业应用工作者和学生踊跃投稿，参加会议。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoPlainText" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 3.9pt;" align="left"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">会议期间将举办数字化设计制造和服务等制造业信息化软件系统，图形软件和硬件、计算机及</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">IT</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">技术新产品展示会和专题报告会，欢迎有关公司、厂商、院校和研究单位报名参展。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoPlainText" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: 24px; margin-top: 7.8pt;" align="left"><span style="font-size: 15pt; line-height: 30px; font-family: 黑体;">二、大会主办协办单位，时间地点</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoPlainText" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 3.9pt;" align="left"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">会议名称：第三届中国图学大会</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">    China Graphics’2011</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoPlainText" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 3.9pt;" align="left"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">主办单位：中国图学学会</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoPlainText" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 3.9pt;" align="left"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">承办单位：西南交通大学、中国图学学会应用图学专业委员会</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoPlainText" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 3.9pt;" align="left"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">协办单位：四川大学、电子科技大学、《计算机集成制造系统－</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">CIMS</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">》编辑部、《工程图学学报》编辑部、相关企业和其他新闻媒体</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoPlainText" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 3.9pt;" align="left"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">会议时间：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">2011</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">8</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">18</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">－</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">21</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">日</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoPlainText" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 3.9pt;" align="left"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">会议地点：四川省成都市</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoPlainText" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: 24px; margin-top: 7.8pt;" align="left"><span style="font-size: 15pt; line-height: 30px; font-family: 黑体;">三、大会征文范围（包括但不限于）</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoPlainText" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: 20pt; margin-bottom: 7.8pt;" align="left"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">会议征文范围参考下表：</span></p>\r\n<div style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;" align="center">\r\n<table id="table1" class="MsoNormalTable" style="font-size: 10pt; width: 783.2000122070313px; border-collapse: collapse;" border="0" width="99%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style="height: 14.2pt;">\r\n<td style="width: 139.9pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.2pt;" width="187">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 21pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">图学理论、方法和技术</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 150.35pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.2pt;" width="200">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -21pt; margin-left: 21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">计算机动画</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 129.5pt; padding: 0cm; height: 14.2pt;" width="173">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 21pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">三维数据获取</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="height: 14.2pt;">\r\n<td style="width: 139.9pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.2pt;" width="187">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 21pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">图学应用</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 150.35pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.2pt;" width="200">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -21pt; margin-left: 21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">计算机仿真</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 129.5pt; padding: 0cm; height: 14.2pt;" width="173">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 21pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">三维重建</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="height: 14.2pt;">\r\n<td style="width: 139.9pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.2pt;" width="187">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 21pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">图学教育的理论与实践</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 150.35pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.2pt;" width="200">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -21pt; margin-left: 21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">计算机视觉</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 129.5pt; padding: 0cm; height: 14.2pt;" width="173">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 21pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">模型轻量化及可视化技术</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="height: 14.2pt;">\r\n<td style="width: 139.9pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.2pt;" width="187">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 21pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">图学发展史</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 150.35pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.2pt;" width="200">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">科学计算与工程信息可视化</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 129.5pt; padding: 0cm; height: 14.2pt;" width="173">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">交互式模型虚拟拆装技术</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="height: 14.2pt;">\r\n<td style="width: 139.9pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.2pt;" width="187">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 21pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">几何计算</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 150.35pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.2pt;" width="200">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 21pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">虚拟现实</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 129.5pt; padding: 0cm; height: 14.2pt;" width="173">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 21pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体;">CAD/CAE/CAPP/CAM</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">技术</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="height: 14.2pt;">\r\n<td style="width: 139.9pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.2pt;" width="187">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 21pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">几何表达</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 150.35pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.2pt;" width="200">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -21pt; margin-left: 21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">基于网格的建模与绘制</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 129.5pt; padding: 0cm; height: 14.2pt;" width="173">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -21pt; margin-left: 21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">协同仿真技术</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="height: 14.2pt;">\r\n<td style="width: 139.9pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.2pt;" width="187">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 21pt; text-indent: -21pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">图形和