(17, 69, '上海市工程图学学会召开2010年学术年会', '2010', '<p style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; line-height: 24px;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;"> 2010年12月26日上海市工程图学学会在东华大学召开了2010年学术年会，来自上海各高校、部分高职、中专职校、工厂及研究所的100余名代表欢聚一堂。上午大会由李金海秘书长主持，首先东华大学机械学院领导陈革教授代表学会挂靠单位东华大学向大会致辞，随后理事长杨建国教授作了学会年度工作报告及题为“数字化设计与制造——图学应用的广阔天地|”的学术报告，接着上海交通大学何援军教授作了题为“几何计算”的|学术报告，学会副理事长、华东理工大学林大钧教授作了“抓住机遇，致力实践，推进图学事业又好又快的发展”的学术报告，最后由学会合作单位——广州中望龙腾软件公司上海教育事业部技术代表介绍了中望3D及中望CAD国产设计软件。下午学会组织了3个分会场进行学术交流，来自各高校的16名专家教授作了学术交流报告，会场交流互动，气氛异常活跃。会议结束后很多代表表示这次会议办得很精彩，通过学术交流加强了会员之间的沟通和交流，使大家收获匪浅。</span></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; line-height: 24px;"> </p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/IMGP1847.JPG" alt="" width="476" height="359" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/DSC00803.JPG" alt="" width="410" height="546" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/DSC00799.JPG" alt="" width="432" height="572" border="0" /> </p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/IMGP1855.JPG" alt="" width="477" height="358" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/IMGP1857.JPG" alt="" width="481" height="363" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/IMGP1861.JPG" alt="" width="482" height="363" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/IMGP1865.JPG" alt="" width="494" height="369" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/IMGP1876.JPG" alt="" width="496" height="373" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/IMGP1878.JPG" alt="" width="494" height="372" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: 24px;" align="center"><img style="display: block;" src="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/IMGP1882.JPG" alt="" width="494" height="370" border="0" /></p>', 1, 10, '2014-07-31 07:07:40', 550, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-07-31 07:07:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","sh