(18, 70, '上海市工程图学学会 ', '2014-07-31-07-10-51', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; line-height: 20pt;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 18pt; font-family: 黑体;">上海市工程图学学会</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; line-height: 20pt;" align="center"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21.600000381469727px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 50.666664123535156px;">沪图学会〔</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21.600000381469727px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 50.666664123535156px;">2010</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21.600000381469727px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 50.666664123535156px;">〕</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21.600000381469727px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 50.666664123535156px;">1</span><span lang="en-us" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21.600000381469727px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 50.666664123535156px;">6</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21.600000381469727px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 50.666664123535156px;">号</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; line-height: 20pt;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">关于工程制图课程教学资源库建设项目申报的通知</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; line-height: 18pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">各有关学校：</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">教育部实施的“卓越工程师培养计划”对各个工科院校而言是一个崭新的课题<span lang="EN-US">,</span>而在工程师的培养过程中，工程制图是最重要的基础之一，为了夯实这一基础，上海市工程图学学会将依托行业优势，开展工程制图课程教学资源库建设，请各工科院校认真组织申报工作，现将有关事项通知如下。</span></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm;"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; line-height: 18pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm;"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">一、项目组织机构</span></b></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">项目组织机构由上海市工程图学学会、项目创作委员会、华东理工大学出版社组成。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">项目主办单位为上海市工程图学学会。主要实施项目审批、对项目创作委员会提交的工程制图课程教学资源库进行审核，承担资源库发行，成果分配等职责。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">项目创作委员会由各项目负责人及相关技术人员组成。主要承担制定项目技术要求，按照要求完成所报项目的建设内容，整合各个模块的内容等职责。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">工程制图课程教学资源库出版单位为华东理工大学出版社。主要负责资源库出版工作。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; line-height: 18pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">二、<b>项目建设内容与成果形式</b></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; line-height: 18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">1.</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">项目建设内容</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">项目建设内容由工程制图习题解析；课程设计成套图纸；毕业设计成套图纸； 典型企业成套图纸；制图大赛成套图纸等模块组成。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">选择工程制图习题解析模块的项目，应提交本校工程制图课程习题及解析与答案；选择课程设计成套图纸模块的项目应提交本校机械设计课程及相关专业课程的课程设计的三维、二维成套图纸及相应的视频动画；选择毕业设计成套图纸模块的项目应提交本校相关专业毕业设计课题的三维、二维成套图纸及相应的视频动画；选择典型企业成套图纸模块的项目应与企业联系，提交企业典型设备、机器的三维、二维成套图纸及相应的视频动画；选择制图大赛成套图纸模块的项目应与企业联系，提交历届全国制图大赛的三维、二维成套图纸及自己创作设计的大赛图纸。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; line-height: 18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">2</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">．项目成果形式</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">工程制图课程教学资源库建设已经纳入“十二五”国家重点音像、电子出版物出版规划项目，资源库将以光盘形式由华东理工大学出版社出版，上海市工程图学学会负责发行，面向学习工程制图课程的广大学生，为他们将来成为卓越工程师打下坚实基础。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">三、<b>申报条件</b></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">1</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">．申报工程制图课程教学资源库建设项目要求</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">（<span lang="EN-US">1</span>）资源库原则上按本科、高职高专、中专技校分类建设。申报者经所在单位批准，选择参与建设的内容。原则上每位项目负责人申报的建设内容不超过二项。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">（<span lang="EN-US">2</span>）项目负责人为学校专职教师，具有副教授及以上职称，且近<span lang="EN-US">3</span>年主讲工程制图课程不少于<span lang="EN-US">2</span>轮。项目负责人只能是<span lang="EN-US">1</span>名，负责组织团队，填写“十二五”工程制图课程教学资源库建设项目申报表，领导团队开展项目建设。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">2</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">．项目负责人要承诺申报材料的真实性，引用的项目资源要注明来源，内容不侵犯他人的知识产权。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">3. </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">工程制图课程教学资源库视为职务作品。凡申请工程制图课程教学资源库项目建设的学校将被视为同意本校参与该项目建设的人员享受出版物作者的权利。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">4</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">．项目申报学校要为申报项目提供建设经费，申报项目被批准后，要保证质量、按时完成所承担的建设内容。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; line-height: 18pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm;"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">四、申报办法</span></b></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">1. </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">各学校可以由工程制图课程或相关课程负责人组织本校教师或联系他校教师进行申报，也鼓励其同时向所在学校申请本校组织的教改项目，进行立项建设。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">2</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">．鼓励各校有教学资源库建设基础的教师联合申报。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">3</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">．申报者需填写《上海市工程图学学会“十二五”工程制图课程教学资源库建设项目申报表》，经所在单位同意盖章后寄到：上海市延安西路<span lang="EN-US">1882</span>号上海市工程图学学会秘书处（邮编<span lang="EN-US">200051</span>），</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;"><a style="color: blue; text-decoration: underline;" href="mailto:%E5%B9%B6%E5%B0%86%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E7%89%88%E5%8F%91%E9%80%81%E5%88%B0shegs@dhu.edu.cn"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: black; text-decoration: none;">并<span lang="EN-US">将电子版发送到shegs@dhu.edu.cn</span></span></a></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">4</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">．项目申报截止日期：<span lang="EN-US">2010</span>年<span lang="EN-US">12</span>月<span lang="EN-US">30</span>日</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">5. </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">学会秘书处电话：<span lang="EN-US">62373322</span>；传真：<span lang="EN-US">62379434</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 234pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 234pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">上海市工程图学学会</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; text-indent: 240pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">2010</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">年<span lang="EN-US">11</span>月<span lang="EN-US">30</span>日</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; text-align: center; line-height: 20pt;"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;"><span style="font-size: 16pt;"><a href="http://shegs.dhu.edu.cn/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%88%B6%E5%9B%BE%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E6%95%99%E5%AD%A6%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E5%BA%93%E7%AB%8B%E9%A1%B9%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E8%A1%A8.doc">附:工程制图课程教学资源库建设项目申报表</a></span></span></p>', 1, 10, '2014-07-31 07:10:51', 550, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-07-31 07:10:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 1, 5, '', '', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(19, 71, '上海市工程图学学会', '2014-07-31-07-12-59', '<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21.600000381469727px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 50.666664123535156px; text-align: center;">沪图学会〔</span><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #000000; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21.600000381469727px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 50.666664123535156px; text-align: center;">2010</span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21.600000381469727px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 50.666664123535156px; text-align: center;">〕</span><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #000000; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21.600000381469727px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 50.666664123535156px; text-align: center;">1</span><span lang="en-us" style="color: #000000; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21.600000381469727px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 50.666664123535156px; text-align: center;">5</span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21.600000381469727px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 50.666664123535156px; text-align: center;">号</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: center;" align="center"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: x-large;">收缴会费的通知</span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: 宋体;">各位会员：</span></p>\r\n<blockquote style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: center;">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: 宋体;">根据学会第八届理事会第三次会议研究决定，本年度会费标准调整如下：</span></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: 宋体;">1.普通会员30元/年；</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: 宋体;">2.高级会员40元/年；</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: 宋体;">3.本届理事会理事50元/年；</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: 宋体;">4.年龄在70周岁及以上的会员免交会费。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: 宋体;">本年度会费收缴时间为，即日起至2011年1月31日。请各位会员将会费交至：</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: underline;">上海市延安西路1882号上海市工程图学学会办公室或交至各单位会员联络员。</span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: center;"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: 宋体;">    按时缴纳会费是每个会员的义务，希望各位会员自觉缴纳。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: 宋体;">    特此通知。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: center; margin-left: 21.75pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 15pt;">                     </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 180pt; margin-left: 21.75pt;"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: 宋体;">上海市工程图学学会秘书处</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: #000000; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: center; margin-left: 21.75pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 15pt;">                                                                      2010<